metadata.name: The Justiciar Supreme
metadata.description:
"A leader who uses wisdom and fairness to guide their people. He strives to ensure that justice is upheld and that the laws are fair and respected. Known for his courage, decisiveness, and ability to lead with integrity."

My 1st and oldest OCs Hail Mallory having a new concept design using Midjourney AI V4. He's part of The Inexplicit story my colleague and I were writing the past decade. Thanks to the new tools and mediums the fantasy worlds we created can be brought to life like never before. 

A long-lasting dream of visualizing the story finally coming true is an amazing feeling. It is like a door to possibility has opened, allowing for the realization of something that was once only imagined. It can be both incredibly exciting and overwhelming, as there will now be opportunities available to explore and develop the story further. 
The joy of seeing the dream come alive is unlike any other.  
Really hope it will be appreciated.
